 more positional versatility, as Morgan operates primarily as a true No.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\", \"score\": 0.9720468675461683, \"rank\": 0.0278401578028532, \"text\": \"Morgan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic roster\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"just 18 spots\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"Hayes\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"more positional versatility\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"a true No\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"9. \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was a tough decision of course, especially considering Alex\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s history and her record with this team but I felt I wanted to go in another direction and selected other players,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Hayes, speaking with media members after Wednesday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s roster reveal.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough decision\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"her record\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"this team\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"another direction\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"other players\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"Hayes\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"media members\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"roster reveal\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHaving a roster that could adapt is essential.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a roster\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a tight turnaround between games.\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tight turnaround\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So of course, having players on the roster that could play more than one position mattered with squad depth.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The USWNT coach also opted for youth, naming nine first-time Olympians to her roster, including defender Jenna Nighswonger, midfielder Sam Coffey and forward Jaedyn Shaw.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1538, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\", \"score\": 0.99897483665153, \"rank\": 0.0010117873498063272, \"text\": \"Jenna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\"}, {\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Coffey\", \"score\": 0.9999918307759698, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Coffey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Coffey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Coffey\"}, {\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.999999964791187, \"rank\": 3.52060099032007e-08, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"the roster\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"more than one position\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"squad depth.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"youth\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"nine first-time Olympians\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"her roster\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just 10 players from the U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 2023 World Cup campaign will be on the plane to Paris, and only eight holdovers remain from the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009920 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996052793, \"rank\": 3.9450983410447814e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Just 10 players\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 2023 World Cup campaign\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"the plane\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"only eight holdovers\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009920 Olympics\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOne of the biggest things for me ever since I got the job was I want to provide opportunities for less experienced players.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOne\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest things\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"less experienced players\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was such a big gap from the top experienced and the rest, and we really have to bring that up,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Hayes.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a big gap\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"Hayes\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe volume of players that haven\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t played more than 30 caps was really, really noticeable for me.\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe volume\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 30 caps\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So the last eight months have been about giving experiences to bridge that gap because there is a correlation between caps played and success in international tournaments.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Crystal Dunn is among the few veterans on the team, but she will be filling a much different role at the Paris Games than she has in previous World Cups and Olympics.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last eight months\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"experiences\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"that gap\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"a correlation\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"caps\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"international tournaments.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Crystal Dunn\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"the few veterans\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"a much different role\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"previous World Cups\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moving up the pitch and into the attack, Dunn adds variability to the front line as a player who has spent most of her USWNT career playing at outside back.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2559, \"end\": 2564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"the attack\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"Dunn\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"variability\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2502}, {\"ngram\": \"the front line\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a testament to Dunn that she has consistently been named to major tournament rosters in a position that is not her preferred place on the pitch (nor her best).\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"a testament\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"Dunn\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"major tournament rosters\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"her preferred place\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Games provides the 31-year-old with a massive stage to showcase the attacking prowess she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s exhibited at the club level for nearly a decade.\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 Games\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive stage\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"the attacking prowess\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"the club level\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly a decade\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If there were any other surprises on the roster, it would be the inclusion of midfielder Korbin Albert, who many considered a bubble player heading into the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 3083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3013, \"end\": 3019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bloom\", \"score\": 0.8479185294773457, \"rank\": 0.17935852074132225, \"text\": \"Albert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bloom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bloom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any other surprises\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"the roster\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"the inclusion\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"a bubble player\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3056}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been receiving consistent call-ups into USWNT camps since late 2023 and has racked up 11 appearances with the squad.\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3132, \"end\": 3137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"h